ize: 16px; font-family: Poppins;\">In Cambodia we know it can be difficult access to information regarding business registration and tax responsibilities, this website aims to provide all this info for free in a clear and detailed way. We cover every step of business registration from what documents you need to register to what are your responsibilities following registration. We hope to be able to help you make an informed decision about business and tax registration in Cambodia.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Poppins;\">This project is an initiative of SHE Investments, a social enterprise which supports Cambodian female entrepreneurs to scale their business, and it has been made possible thanks to the support of USAID, Development Innovations and Ezecom.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_section full_width=\"stretch_row_content\" content_placement=\"middle\" css=\".vc_custom_1558804300719{padding-bottom: 20px !important;}\"][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" wrap_container=\"yes\" css=\".vc_custom_1558804262070{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"Partners\" main_heading_color=\"#4a4a4a\" sub_heading_color=\"#4a4a4a\" main_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Poppins|font_call:Poppins|variant:700\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:700;\" sub_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Poppins|font_call:Poppins|variant:300\" sub_heading_style=\"font-weight:300;\" sub_heading_line_height=\"desktop:35px;\" sub_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:10px;\" sub_heading_font_size=\"desktop:15px;tablet:15px;tablet_portrait:13px;mobile_landscape:10px;mobile:10px;\"][/ultimate_heading][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row wrap_container=\"yes\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"373\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" hover_effect=\"yes\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Poppins;\">SHE Investments supports women with micro businesses to scale to sustainable and impactful SMEs, because they believe that this is where real and long-term social and economic impact can be made. The SME sector is the backbone of any economy, but it’s also a very male-dominated one.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row wrap_container=\"yes\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"371\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" hover_effect=\"yes\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Poppins;\">EZECOM was founded in 2007 to serve the rapidly expanding business and home user internet market in Cambodia. Today it is a leading provider of a wide variety of innovative communication services, including fibre optic, VoIP, virtual private networks and other Internet-based &amp; Cloud solutions. EZECOM owns the fibre optic company Telcotech, which brought very fast and more reliable Internet to Cambodia through the Malaysia-Cambodia-Thailand undersea cable system and its diverse international connectivity.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row wrap_container=\"yes\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"375\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" hover_effect=\"yes\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Poppins;\">USAID is the lead U.S. Government agency that works to end extreme global poverty and enable resilient, democratic societies to realize their potential. In Cambodia, USAID works with local and international partners on a broad range of programs designed to benefit all Cambodians.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row wrap_container=\"yes\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][vc_single_image image=\"369\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" hover_effect=\"yes\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\"][vc_column_text]<span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Poppins;\">Development Innovations is a five-year project fun