INSERT INTO `nge_posts` VALUES('915', '1', '2019-06-18 22:43:54', '2019-06-18 15:43:54', '<h2>Why are you starting a business?</h2>		\n		<p>One of the questions that we ask the most when working with business owners is, “why are you starting this business?”.</p><p>We ask this question as it provides direction for the growth of the business. There are many different answers to this question, such as;</p><ul><li>Making money – either through profit or from selling the business. If you are planning on making money through selling the business, this needs to be clear from the start.</li><li>Lifestyle – owning a business can let you have a more flexible lifestyle, yes you may work more hours, but they can be on your terms. Additionally, knowing what lifestyle you want will direct how you set up the business, such as whether you have someone running the day to day operations of whether you, as the owner will take that role on.</li><li>Passion – for many business owners, they are very passionate about their business idea, product or service and want to share that with as many people as possible.</li><li>Ownership – for some business owners it’s about being in control and being able to make all the important decisions themselves. You can control what happens in the business and if it fails it’s on you but if it succeeds then that’s also on you.</li></ul> <em>Listen to Tex Simheang from Kei Meas talk about her passion for her business and why it drives her</em>https://youtu.be/5yJqBz1LUXo<p>Knowing why you are starting the business and being clear on where you want the business to be in 3-5 years is really important at the start of your journey as this will help guide you on many tough decisions in the future.</p><p> </p><p><em>For more on Goal setting, see the SMART Goals video in the E-learning section of our website.</em></p>', 'Why are you starting a business', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'why-are-you-starting-a-business', '', '', '2019-07-23 11:13:17', '2019-07-23 04:13:17', '', '0', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/?page_id=915', '0', 'page', '', '0');
