024px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					E-VAT\n				</h3>\n				<p>Here is a brief overview of how to use the newly released E-VAT system</p>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/e-vat/\" role=\"button\">\n						Read more here\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"618\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0307-1024x618.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0307-1024x618.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0307-300x181.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0307-768x463.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0307-640x386.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0307-400x241.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0307-367x221.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n			<h2>NEED HELP?</h2>		\n			<p>Our partners can help provide you with your monthly tax need</p>		\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/contact-us/\" role=\"button\">\n						See HERE\n					</a>', 'Monthly Taxes & Obligations', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'compliance-and-registration-checklist-3', '', '', '2019-07-23 11:10:59', '2019-07-23 04:10:59', '', '0', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/?page_id=1159', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `nge_posts` VALUES('1160', '1', '2019-06-20 21:02:33', '2019-06-20 14:02:33', '<h2>Business Licences</h2>		\n		<p>Depending on your business activity you may be required to obtain a licence from the relevant ministry</p>		\n				<h3>\n					What are Licences?\n				</h3>\n				<p>A license is an authorization for you to run your business, the licenses you require depends on your business activity. It is your duty as the business owner to know which ministry you have to get a license from, often you will not be notified of what licenses you require.\nWhich licenses you require is not always clear and often you may need to get licenses from more than 1 ministry. For example, if you have a restaurant, you will need a license from the ministry of tourism but you may also have to get in touch with the Ministry of Health and the Fire Station for safety reasons.\nThe cost depends on the licenses you need. In general, they have to be renewed every year. Not getting these licences could lead to a fine, or in worse cases, to the closing of your business.\nLicenses depend on what your business activities are and also what type of goods you trade. As your business grows and changes, it is your responsibility to ensure you have the correct licences for your new activities.\n</p>\n			<figure><a href=\"www.mih.gov.kh\"><img width=\"226\" height=\"223\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MIH-logo.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MIH-logo.jpeg 226w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MIH-logo-85x85.jpeg 85w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MIH-logo-50x50.jpeg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 226px) 100vw, 226px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"www.mih.gov.kh\">Manufacturing</a></h3><p>For any type of manafacturing or handicraft you will need obtain a licence from the Ministry of Industry and Handicraft</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"https://www.tourismcambodia.org/public/index.php/the-ministry\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"130\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MOT-cambodia.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"https://www.tourismcambodia.org/public/index.php/the-ministry\">Tour companies, spas, restaurants</a></h3><p>All business that serve tourists need to obtain a licence from the Ministry of Tourism, including bars, restaurants, KTV\'s and hotels.</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"http://web.maff.gov.kh/\"><img width=\"264\" height=\"275\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MAFF_Cambodia.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"http://web.maff.gov.kh/\">Agriculture, Fruit &amp; Veg, Butcher</a></h3><p>For any business related to agriculture, forestry &amp; fisheries you must obtain a licence from the Ministry of Agriculture, Forestries &amp; Fisheries</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"moh.gov.kh\"><img width=\"250\" height=\"273\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MOH_logo.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"moh.gov.kh\">Doctors, Pharmacies, Physiotherapy</a></h3><p>Any businesses related to the provision of health services are required to obtain a licence from the Ministry of Health</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"mef.gov.kh\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MEF_Cambodia.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MEF_Cambodia.png 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MEF_Cambodia-150x150.png 150w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MEF_Cambodia-85x85.png 85w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MEF_Cambodia-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"mef.gov.kh\">Real Estate Services</a></h3><p>If you provide any real estate services you will need to obtain a license from the Ministry of Economy and Finance</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"mlmupc.gov.kh\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mlmupc.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mlmupc.png 225w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mlmupc-150x150.png 150w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mlmupc-85x85.png 85w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mlmupc-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"mlmupc.gov.kh\">Contruction Companies</a></h3><p>Any construction business needs to obtain a licence from the Ministry of Land Management, Urban Planning & Construction</p>		\n			<h2>NEED HELP?</h2>		\n			<p>Our team at Ngeay Ngeay can take care of all your registration needs</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						Contact Us\n					</a>', 'Business Licences', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1084-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-20 21:02:33', '2019-06-20 14:02:33', '', '1084', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/2019/06/20/1084-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `nge_posts` VALUES('1161', '1', '2019-06-20 21:09:07', '2019-06-20 14:09:07', '<h2>Compliance Checklist</h2>\nEverything you need to know to be compliant with the Cambodian Law\n\n<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\nPart 2: Taxes\n</a>\n<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\nPart 3: Labour Law\n</a>\n<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\nUpdates\n</a>\n<h2>Part 1: Registration</h2>\n<h3>\n					Ministry of Commerce\n\nRegistration</h3>\nThe first step to compliance is to register with the Ministry of Commerce. See our detailed guide on how to register with the MoC here\n\n<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/registering-a-business-checklist-good/\" role=\"button\">\nRead more here\n</a>\n<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0835-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0835-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0835-300x200.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0835-768x512.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0835-640x427.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0835-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0835-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\">\n<h3>\n					General Department of Tax\n\nRegistration</h3>\nOnce you have completed the Ministry of Commerce registration, you need to register with the GDT.\n\n<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/registering-a-business-checklist-good/\" role=\"button\">\nRead more here\n</a>\n<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-300x200.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-768x512.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-640x427.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\">\n<h3>\n					Ministry of Labour\n\nRegistration</h3>\nTo be compliant with the Labour Laws of Cambodia you need to register with the Ministry of Labour, see our guide here\n\n<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\nRead more here\n</a>\n<img width=\"570\" height=\"329\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22.jpg 570w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22-300x173.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22-400x231.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22-367x212.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\">\n<h3>\n					National Social Security Fund</h3>\nThe NSSF is the social security fund for Cambodia, and registration with NSSF needs to be completed after you have registered with the Ministry of Labour\n\n<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\nRead more here\n</a>\n<img width=\"570\" height=\"329\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-23.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-23.jpg 570w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-23-300x173.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-23-400x231.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-23-367x212.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\">\n<h2><a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Registering-a-Business-Checklist.pdf\">Download our Checklist Here</a></h2>\n<h5>Our detailed, Printable checklist will help you simplify the registration process</h5>\n<h3>\n					Licences</h3>\nDepending on the nature of your business you may be required to obtain a licence from one or more of the ministries\n\n<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/documents-2/\" role=\"button\">\nRead more here\n</a>\n<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-300x200.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-768x512.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-640x427.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\">\n<h3>\n					Export</h3>\nMany business owners want to export their products internationally, to do this there are a few steps required\n\n<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/elementor-746-2-2/\" role=\"button\">\nRead more here\n</a>\n<img width=\"570\" height=\"329\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22.jpg 570w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22-300x173.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22-400x231.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22-367x212.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\">\n<h2>NEED HELP?</h2>\nOur team at Ngeay Ngeay can take care of all your registration needs\n\n<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\nContact Us\n</a>', 'Compliance Checklist: Part 1', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1159-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-20 21:09:07', '2019-06-20 14:09:07', '', '1159', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/2019/06/20/1159-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
