e the newly released E-VAT system\n\n<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\nRead more here\n</a>\n<img width=\"570\" height=\"329\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22.jpg 570w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22-300x173.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22-400x231.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22-367x212.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\">\n<h2>NEED HELP?</h2>\nOur team at Ngeay Ngeay can take care of all your registration needs\n\n<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\nContact Us\n</a>', 'Monthly Taxes & Obligations', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1159-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-20 21:09:50', '2019-06-20 14:09:50', '', '1159', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/2019/06/20/1159-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `nge_posts` VALUES('1169', '1', '2019-06-20 21:25:48', '2019-06-20 14:25:48', '<h2>E-VAT</h2>		\n		<p>A brief overview of the newly implemented E-VAT system</p>		\n		<p>The E-VAT system is a new system that has been implemented in Cambodia in 2019, to help the government track VAT payments better. To input your information into e-vat go to <a href=\"https://owp.tax.gov.kh:50005/epaymentowpweb/login\">E-VAT Site</a></p><ul><li>Each business will need to create a username and fill in the company information.</li><li>Every business needs to enter every purchase they have been charged VAT for</li><li>Every business needs to upload every sale they have made for the month</li></ul><p>E-VAT deadline is: 20<sup>th</sup> of each month. You will need to attach the E-VAT documents to your monthly tax return</p>', 'E-VAT', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'e-vat', '', '', '2019-07-26 08:51:26', '2019-07-26 01:51:26', '', '0', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/?page_id=1169', '0', 'page', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `nge_posts` VALUES('1170', '1', '2019-06-20 21:26:05', '2019-06-20 14:26:05', '<h2>Contracts</h2>		\n		<p>There are two types of contracts in Cambodian Labor Law, fixed duration contracts (FDC’s) and Unfixed Duration Contracts (UDC’s).</p>		\n		<p><strong>Fixed Duration Contracts</strong></p><p>These contracts are for a fixed term, and can be anywhere up to 2 years in length. After two years the employer can decide to renew the contract or not renew the contract. A fixed term contract must be in writing.</p><p>If the contract finishes, and the employee continues working without a contract, the employee is understood to be on a UDC</p><p>If a fixed term contract expires or is terminated, the employee has the right to severance pay of 5% of total wages over the contract (Article 73). If a FDC is terminated early, the employer is required to payout the entire the value of the contract.</p><p><strong>Unfixed Duration Contracts</strong></p><p>Unfixed duration contracts are for an unspecified amount of time and can be either verbal or written.</p><p>For terminating a UDC  the minimum period of notice is:</p><ul><li>Seven days, if the worker\'s length of continuous service is less than six months;</li><li>Fifteen days, if the worker\'s length of continuous service is from six months to two years;</li><li>One month, if the worker\'s length of continuous service is longer than two years and up to five years.</li><li>Two months, if the worker\'s length of continuous service is longer than five years and up to ten years.</li><li>Three months, if the worker\'s length of continuous service is longer than then years.</li></ul><p>Seniority payments are also applicable to UDC’s. For more information please see the Seniority Payments section</p>', 'E-VAT', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1169-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-20 21:26:05', '2019-06-20 14:26:05', '', '1169', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/2019/06/20/1169-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `nge_posts` VALUES('1171', '1', '2019-06-20 21:27:56', '2019-06-20 14:27:56', '<h2>E-VAT</h2>		\n		<p>A brief overview of the newly implemented E-VAT system</p>		\n		<p>The E-VAT system is a new system that has been implemented in Cambodia in 2019, to help the government track VAT payments better. To input your information into e-vat go to: </p><p><a href=\"https://owp.tax.gov.kh:50005/epaymentowpweb/login\">https://owp.tax.gov.kh:50005/epaymentowpweb/login</a></p><p> </p><ul><li>Each business will need to create a username and fill in the company information.</li><li>Every business needs to enter every purchase they have been charged VAT for</li><li>Every business needs to upload every sale they have made for the month</li></ul><p>E-VAT deadline is: 20<sup>th</sup> of each month. You will need to attach the E-VAT documents to your monthly tax return</p>', 'E-VAT', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1169-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-20 21:27:56', '2019-06-20 14:27:56', '', '1169', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/2019/06/20/1169-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `nge_posts` VALUES('1172', '1', '2019-06-20 21:32:08', '2019-06-20 14:32:08', '<h2>Import/Export</h2>		\n		<p>To be able to import/export it is important that you have applied for this in your tax patent with the General Department of Tax</p>		\n		<p>For importing and exporting, you need to register your patent as an import/export patent when you register with the General Department of Tax.</p><p>When you are ready to do your first import/export you need to register with the Automated System for Customs Data (ASYCUDA). To do this you will need to go to the customs office located at No. 6-8, Preah Norodom Blvd., Sangkat Phsar Thmei III, Khan Daun Penh, Phnom Penh, Cambodia.</p><p>If you are importing/exporting any items deemed sensitive by the government then you will need to obtain a licence from the relevant ministry. </p>		\n			<iframe frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" src=\"https://maps.google.com/maps?q=customs%20office%2C%20phnom%20penh&amp;t=m&amp;z=14&amp;output=embed&amp;iwloc=near\" aria-label=\"customs office, phnom penh\"></iframe>', 'Export', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'export', '', '', '2019-06-24 16:40:45', '2019-06-24 09:40:45', '', '0', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/?page_id=1172', '0', 'page', '', '0');
