INSERT INTO `nge_posts` VALUES('1533', '1', '2019-06-24 16:39:46', '2019-06-24 09:39:46', '<h2>Business Licences</h2>		\n		<p>Depending on your business activity you may be required to obtain a licence from the relevant ministry</p>		\n				<h3>\n					What are Licences?\n				</h3>\n				<p>A license is an authorization for you to run your business, the licenses you require depends on your business activity. It is your duty as the business owner to know which ministry you have to get a license from, often you will not be notified of what licenses you require.\nWhich licenses you require is not always clear and often you may need to get licenses from more than 1 ministry. For example, if you have a restaurant, you will need a license from the Ministry of Tourism but you may also have to get in touch with the Ministry of Health and the Fire Station for safety reasons.\nThe cost depends on the licenses you need. In general, they have to be renewed every year. Not getting these licences could lead to a fine, or in worse cases, to the closing of your business.\nLicenses depend on what your business activities are and also what type of goods you trade. As your business grows and changes, it is your responsibility to ensure you have the correct licences for your new activities.\n</p>\n			<figure><a href=\"www.mih.gov.kh\"><img width=\"226\" height=\"223\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MIH-logo.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MIH-logo.jpeg 226w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MIH-logo-85x85.jpeg 85w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MIH-logo-50x50.jpeg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 226px) 100vw, 226px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"www.mih.gov.kh\">Manufacturing</a></h3><p>For any type of manafacturing or handicraft you will need obtain a licence from the Ministry of Industry and Handicraft</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"https://www.tourismcambodia.org/public/index.php/the-ministry\"><img width=\"150\" height=\"130\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MOT-cambodia.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"https://www.tourismcambodia.org/public/index.php/the-ministry\">Tour companies, spas, restaurants</a></h3><p>All business that serve tourists need to obtain a licence from the Ministry of Tourism, including bars, restaurants, KTV\'s and hotels.</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"http://web.maff.gov.kh/\"><img width=\"264\" height=\"275\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MAFF_Cambodia.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"http://web.maff.gov.kh/\">Agriculture, Fruit &amp; Veg, Butcher</a></h3><p>For any business related to agriculture, forestry &amp; fisheries you must obtain a licence from the Ministry of Agriculture, Forestries &amp; Fisheries</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"moh.gov.kh\"><img width=\"250\" height=\"273\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MOH_logo.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"moh.gov.kh\">Doctors, Pharmacies, Physiotherapy</a></h3><p>Any businesses related to the provision of health services are required to obtain a licence from the Ministry of Health</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"mef.gov.kh\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MEF_Cambodia.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MEF_Cambodia.png 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MEF_Cambodia-150x150.png 150w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MEF_Cambodia-85x85.png 85w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/MEF_Cambodia-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"mef.gov.kh\">Real Estate Services</a></h3><p>If you provide any real estate services you will need to obtain a license from the Ministry of Economy and Finance</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"mlmupc.gov.kh\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mlmupc.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mlmupc.png 225w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mlmupc-150x150.png 150w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mlmupc-85x85.png 85w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/mlmupc-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"mlmupc.gov.kh\">Contruction Companies</a></h3><p>Any construction business needs to obtain a licence from the Ministry of Land Management, Urban Planning & Construction</p>		\n			<h2>NEED HELP?</h2>		\n			<p>Our team at Ngeay Ngeay can take care of all your registration needs</p>		\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/contact-us/\" role=\"button\">\n						Contact Us\n					</a>', 'Business Licences', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1084-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-24 16:39:46', '2019-06-24 09:39:46', '', '1084', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/2019/06/24/1084-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `nge_posts` VALUES('1535', '1', '2019-06-24 16:39:51', '2019-06-24 09:39:51', '<h2>Annual Taxes</h2>		\n		<p>Every year on the 31st of March annual taxes need to be filed for every business. This is quite a complex process and we recommend hiring a professional firm to assist</p>		\n		<p><strong>Annual tax on profit</strong></p><p>At the end of the year, you will have to pay a tax for a total amount of 20% of your profit. You can then deduce the 1% you paid every month during the year.<br /><br /></p><p>Annual taxable profit in USD for a limited company:<br />&lt; 1,463 USD                     0%<br />1,463 – 3,658 USD          5%<br />3,658 – 24,878 USD       10%<br />24,878 – 36,585 USD     15%<br />&gt; 36,585 USD                   20%</p><p> </p><p><strong>Small Taxpayers</strong></p><p>The patent tax for sole proprietorships and partnerships is $100, which is approx. KHR400,000.</p><p><strong>Medium &amp; Large Taxpayers</strong></p><p>The patent tax is a fixed annual fee. It depends on which taxpayer category your company belongs to (small, medium or large). These are the official patent tax amounts:</p><p>Medium Taxpayer          KHR1,200,000/USD300</p><p>Large Taxpayer             KHR3,000,000 or KHR5,000,000*/ USD750 or USD1,250</p><p>*If the annual turnover of the Large Taxpayer exceeds KHR10,000 million (USD2.5 million) then the Patent Tax payable will be USD1,250.</p><p>If the annual turnover of the Large Taxpayer is less than KHR10,000 million (USD2.5 million) the Patent Tax payable will be USD750.</p>', 'Annual Taxes', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1186-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-24 16:39:51', '2019-06-24 09:39:51', '', '1186', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/2019/06/24/1186-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `nge_posts` VALUES('1537', '1', '2019-06-24 16:39:57', '2019-06-24 09:39:57', '<h2>Business Status</h2>		\n		<p>Before you register you need to choose your business status carefully as it can be difficult to change, once you have registered</p>		\n		<p><strong>SOLE PROPRIETORSHIP</strong></p><p>Registering as a sole proprietorship means that one person owns and operates the business. This person owns the whole capital and receives all the profits of the company. It also means that all obligations and liabilities are the responsibility of the proprietor. A business registered as a sole proprietorship is considered as a small taxpayer.</p><p>The problem of the sole proprietorship is that you are personally liable for the business but if your business is small and risk of having large debts/liabilities is small, then registering as a sole proprietorship may be the best choice to pay less taxes. Currently, it is difficult for foreigners to be small taxpayers, however they can be registered as a sole proprietorship</p>		\n				Sole ProprietorBest for very small businesses with only one owner\nPartnershipBest for very small businesses with two or more ownersLimited Liability CompanyThe most common form of registration, for small to large businesses. This form of business carries the least liability for the owner/s			\n		<p><strong>PARTNERSHIPS</strong></p><p>Two or more persons together can register as a partnership. This is legally similar to a sole proprietorship, however there are two or more people registered as business owners. It is advised to create a written partnership contract to minimise the risk of any issues that may arise. All the partners are responsible for any debts and obligations.</p><p><strong>PRIVATE LIMITED COMPANY</strong></p><p>This legal company status is what most people think of when they think of registering and is composed of shareholders and directors. Shareholders and directors are not personally liable for the company’s debts. A private limited company is composed of 2 to 30 shareholders.</p><p><strong>FOREIGN BRANCH/SUBSIDIARY</strong></p><p>Even if the company has already registered as another company, its subsidiary, branch or representative office has to register in Cambodia. There are three possibilities:</p><ul><li>Create a subsidiary of the foreign parent. It’s a limited company with 51% or more owned by the foreign company</li><li>A branch office can operate to conduct a particular activity. Then, it is the same entity as the parent company, so the parent company is liable for its debts and obligations.</li><li>A representative office can be implemented but cannot buy or sell on the Cambodian territory. This status only permits to make the sourcing of local goods and services easier or to get information for the parent company.</li></ul>', 'Business Status', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '755-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-24 16:39:57', '2019-06-24 09:39:57', '', '755', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/2019/06/24/755-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `nge_posts` VALUES('1539', '1', '2019-06-24 16:40:07', '2019-06-24 09:40:07', '<h2>Compliance Checklist: Part 1</h2>		\n		<p>Everything you need to know to be compliant with the Cambodian Law</p>		\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/compliance-and-registration-checklist-2/\" role=\"button\">\n						Part 2: Taxes\n					</a>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/compliance-checklist-part-3/\" role=\"button\">\n						Part 3: Labour Law\n					</a>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/updates/\" role=\"button\">\n						Updates\n					</a>\n			<h2>Part 1: Registration</h2>		\n				<h3>\n					Ministry of Commerce <br>\n<br>Registration<br>\n				</h3>\n				<p>The first step to compliance is to register with the Ministry of Commerce. See our detailed guide on how to register with the MoC here</p>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/registering-a-business-checklist-good/\" role=\"button\">\n						Read more here\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_6588-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_6588-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_6588-300x200.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_6588-768x512.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_6588-640x427.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_6588-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_6588-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					General Department of Tax <br><br>\nRegistration\n				</h3>\n				<p>Once you have completed the Ministry of Commerce registration, you need to register with the GDT. \n</p>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/registering-a-business-checklist-good/\" role=\"button\">\n						Read more here\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/SOGE1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/SOGE1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/SOGE1-300x200.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/SOGE1-768x512.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/SOGE1-640x427.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/SOGE1-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/SOGE1-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					Ministry of Labour <br><br>\nRegistration\n				</h3>\n				<p>To be compliant with the Labour Laws of Cambodia you need to register with the Ministry of Labour, see our guide here</p>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/ministry-of-labour-registration/\" role=\"button\">\n						Read more here\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5962-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5962-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5962-300x200.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5962-768x512.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5962-640x427.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5962-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5962-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					National Social Security Fund\n				</h3>\n				<p>The NSSF is the social security fund for Cambodia, and registration with NSSF needs to be completed after you have registered with the Ministry of Labour</p>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/nssf-registration/\" role=\"button\">\n						Read more here\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_6528-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_6528-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_6528-300x200.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_6528-768x512.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_6528-640x427.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_6528-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_6528-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n			<h2><a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Registering-a-Business-Checklist.pdf\">Download our Checklist Here</a></h2>		\n			<h5>Our detailed, Printable checklist will help you simplify the registration process</h5>		\n				<h3>\n					Licences\n				</h3>\n				<p>Depending on the nature of your business you may be required to obtain a licence from one or more of the ministries\n</p>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/business-licences/\" role=\"button\">\n						Read more here\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0396-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0396-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0396-300x200.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0396-768x512.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0396-640x427.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0396-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0396-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					Export\n				</h3>\n				<p>Many business owners want to export their products internationally, to do this there are a few steps required</p>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/export/\" role=\"button\">\n						Read more here\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0764-1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0764-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0764-1-300x200.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0764-1-768x512.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0764-1-640x427.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0764-1-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0764-1-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n			<h2>NEED HELP?</h2>		\n			<p>Our team at Ngeay Ngeay can take care of all your registration needs</p>		\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/contact-us/\" role=\"button\">\n						Contact Us\n					</a>', 'Compliance Checklist: Part 1', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1062-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-24 16:40:07', '2019-06-24 09:40:07', '', '1062', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/2019/06/24/1062-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `nge_posts` VALUES('1541', '1', '2019-06-24 16:40:16', '2019-06-24 09:40:16', '<h2>Compliance Checklist: Part 2</h2>		\n		<p>Everything you need to know to be compliant with the Cambodian Law</p>		\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/compliance-and-registration-checklist/\" role=\"button\">\n						Part 1: Registration\n					</a>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/compliance-checklist-part-3/\" role=\"button\">\n						Part 3: Labour Law\n					</a>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/updates/\" role=\"button\">\n						Updates\n					</a>\n			<h2>Part 2: Taxes</h2>		\n				<h3>\n					Monthly Taxes\n				</h3>\n				<p>Everything you need to know about monthly taxes</p>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/compliance-and-registration-checklist-3/\" role=\"button\">\n						Read more here\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0196-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0196-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0196-300x225.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0196-768x576.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0196-463x348.jpg 463w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0196-640x480.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0196-400x300.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0196-367x275.jpg 367w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0196-200x150.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					Annual Taxes\n				</h3>\n				<p>Everything you need to know about annual taxes in Cambodia\n</p>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/annual-taxes/\" role=\"button\">\n						Read more here\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0174-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0174-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0174-300x225.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0174-768x576.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0174-463x348.jpg 463w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0174-640x480.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0174-400x300.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0174-367x275.jpg 367w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0174-200x150.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					Tax Rates\n				</h3>\n				<p>Everything you need to know about tax and NSSF rates in Cambodia</p>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/tax-nssf-rates/\" role=\"button\">\n						Read more here\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0125-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0125-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0125-300x225.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0125-768x576.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0125-463x348.jpg 463w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0125-640x480.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0125-400x300.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0125-367x275.jpg 367w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0125-200x150.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n			<h2>NEED HELP?</h2>		\n			<p>Our team at Ngeay Ngeay can take care of all your registration needs</p>		\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/contact-us/\" role=\"button\">\n						Contact Us\n					</a>', 'Compliance Checklist: Part 2', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1072-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-06-24 16:40:16', '2019-06-24 09:40:16', '