ry business owner we’ve worked with is able to tell us this easily. The second part is harder, we ask them, what is the businesses (or the leaders) passion, or cause, or purpose. This is the WHY, 90% of the businesses we work with have a lot of trouble answering this.</p><p>Sinek, says that most companies will start with the WHAT, then move on to the HOW and sometimes they get to WHY, but great companies will start with WHY as this provides all the reason WHY anyone should follow them, staff or customers. With this in the mind, the WHAT is the proof that belief.</p><p>Can you clearly articulate the WHY of your business? Do your staff now your WHY?</p><p>If you need help providing direction for your business, our team can help</p>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7zFeuSagktM', 'Start with WHY', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1411-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-07-20 12:35:13', '2019-07-20 05:35:13', '', '1411', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/2019/07/20/1411-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
