INSERT INTO `nge_posts` VALUES('1964', '1', '2019-07-24 12:37:36', '2019-07-24 05:37:36', '<h2>Budgets, Cashflow &amp; Your Business</h2>\nKeeping an eye on your cash is critical to survival\n\nWith any young business, cashflow is one of the most important things to understand well. Cashflow is one of the most common reasons that a business will shutdown, sometimes they are even profitable businesses but they if they do manage their cash properly they can go out of business. It is critical that you understand and can track your cashflow.\n\n<strong>Budgets</strong>\n\nThe business budget for a small business is most commonly used when starting your business or going through a significant expansion. Establishing how much capital is needed to either start your business or expand is crucial, because if you do not have enough capital at the start, you can potentially run out of money before your business is profitable. We have a budget template here for you to calculate how much capital you will need to start your business.\n\nTo calculate the capital needed you will need to know:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Estimated start-up expenses</li>\n 	<li>Estimated monthly revenue for the next 6 months</li>\n 	<li>Estimated monthly expenses for the next 6 months</li>\n</ul>\nInput all of these into the template and it will provide an estimated amount of capital needed, included in the budget is some buffer to allow for errors in your estimates.\n\n<strong>Cashflow</strong>\n\nThe cashflow forecast template, can be found here. It includes a 12-week cashflow and a 12-month cashflow, some businesses will require both, for others it will be more appropriate to do one or the other, this will depend on the cashflows of your business.\n\nIt is important when using this template that you ensure the numbers you put in are timed for you either receive or pay the money, not when you are given the invoice or when you make the sale.\n\nThe cashflow forecast should be updated regularly, to ensure that if are having times when you may run out of cash that you can plan accordingly, by delaying bill payments, getting short term loans or chasing up invoices that need to be paid to you.\n\nBy using both the budget template and cashflow template you can get a better handle on how you are spending your money and whether you will have enough money to pay your bills.', 'Budgets, Cashflow & Your Business', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1958-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-07-24 12:37:36', '2019-07-24 05:37:36', '', '1958', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/2019/07/24/1958-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `nge_posts` VALUES('1965', '1', '2019-07-24 16:27:09', '2019-07-24 09:27:09', '<h2>Starting a Business</h2>		\n		<p>What you need to know before you start</p>		\n				<h3>\n					Why are you starting the <br>\n<br>business?\n				</h3>\n				<p>It is very important when you start your business that you know why you are starting it, starting and operating a business is a huge challenge and you can never be 100% prepared for how much hard work it is. Because it is so challenging, it is important to know why you are starting the business, to keep you on track when you face these challenges.<br></p>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/why-are-you-starting-a-business/\" role=\"button\">\n						Read more here\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5904-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5904-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5904-300x200.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5904-768x512.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5904-640x427.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5904-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5904-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					Who is your target market?\n				</h3>\n				<p>This is one of the most important questions you can answer when developing your business model, with out a clear target market your business will struggle. If you try to please everybody you will please no one. Your target market needs to be as specific as possible.\nFor more on defining your target market, click below to go to our e-learning platform</p>\n			<a href=\"learn.ngeayngeay.co\" role=\"button\">\n						Learn more\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5160-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5160-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5160-300x200.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5160-768x512.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5160-640x427.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5160-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5160-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					What is your Value <br><br>\nProposition?\n				</h3>\n				<p>The value proposition, is a promise of value to be delivered and communicated to your customer. What is the value you will deliver to your target market.\nWhy would your target market buy your product or service and not go to a competitor?\nFor more on this topic go to our e-learning platform</p>\n			<a href=\"learn.ngeayngeay.co\" role=\"button\">\n						Learn more\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5898-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5898-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5898-300x200.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5898-768x512.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5898-640x427.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5898-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5898-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					When will you launch?\n				</h3>\n				<p>Having clear timelines around your product development, testing and manufacturing is very important to ensure you can have enough cash flow when beginning your business. How long will it take to be financially sustainable? </p>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-300x225.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-768x576.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-463x348.jpg 463w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-640x480.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-400x300.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-367x275.jpg 367w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-200x150.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n			<h2>How?</h2>		\n			<figure><a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/2019/07/24/elementor-1404-3-3-2-2/\"><img width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465237060_resolutions-11.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465237060_resolutions-11.png 64w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465237060_resolutions-11-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 64px) 100vw, 64px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/2019/07/24/elementor-1404-3-3-2-2/\">Clear Business Model</a></h3><p>For more information go to our article on business models and watch our Business Model Canvas series on the E-learning platform</p>		\n			<figure><img width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465236987_resolutions-16.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465236987_resolutions-16.png 64w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465236987_resolutions-16-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 64px) 100vw, 64px\" /></figure><h3>Complete a Budget</h3><p>See our article and template here on completing a budget</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/elementor-741/\"><img width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\