eay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-300x225.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-768x576.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-463x348.jpg 463w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-640x480.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-400x300.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-367x275.jpg 367w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-200x150.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n			<h2>How?</h2>		\n			<figure><a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/2019/07/24/elementor-1404-3-3-2-2/\"><img width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465237060_resolutions-11.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465237060_resolutions-11.png 64w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465237060_resolutions-11-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 64px) 100vw, 64px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/2019/07/24/elementor-1404-3-3-2-2/\">Clear Business Model</a></h3><p>For more information go to our article on business models and watch our Business Model Canvas series on the E-learning platform</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/2019/07/24/elementor-1404-3-3-2-2-2/\"><img width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465236987_resolutions-16.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465236987_resolutions-16.png 64w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465236987_resolutions-16-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 64px) 100vw, 64px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/2019/07/24/elementor-1404-3-3-2-2-2/\">Complete a Budget</a></h3><p>See our arti