640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/DSCF0253-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					Register through the MoC <br><br>website\n				</h3>\n				<p>Once you have all the documents, you are now ready to register through the Ministry of Commerce website. There are three steps; register as a new user, reserve a name, then proceed to fill out the online form</p>\n			<a href=\"/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay?page_id=800\" role=\"button\">\n						Learn more\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"570\" height=\"329\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22.jpg 570w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22-300x173.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22-400x231.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-22-367x212.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					File Annual Declaration\n				</h3>\n				<p>The Ministry of Commerce registration process is nearly completed, the last step is to file for the annual declaration</p>\n			<a href=\"/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay?page_id=874\" role=\"button\">\n						Learn more\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"570\" height=\"329\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-23.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-23.jpg 570w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-23-300x173.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-23-400x231.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/Layer-23-367x212.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\" />											\n			<h2><a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Registering-a-Business-Checklist.pdf\">Download our Checklist Here</a></h2>		\n			<h5>Our detailed, Printable checklist will help you simplify the registration process</h5>		\n			<h2>General Department of Tax</h2>		\n				<h3>\n					Collect all the documents <br><br>and prerequisites\n				</h3>\n				<p>There are various documents and requirements needed to register at the General Department of Tax, many of which are the same for the MoC. Read our list for everything you require\n</p>\n			<a href=\"/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay?page_id=919\" role=\"button\">\n						Documents & Prerequisites\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0158-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0158-1024x576.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0158-300x169.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0158-768x432.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0158-640x360.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0158-400x225.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0158-367x206.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					Register at the National Tax <br><br>School\n				</h3>\n				<p>The GDT does not have an online registration process at the moment so you are required to go to the National Tax School in person</p>\n			<a href=\"/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay?page_id=925\" role=\"button\">\n						Read more\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0142-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0142-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0142-300x225.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0142-768x576.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0142-463x348.jpg 463w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0142-640x480.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0142-400x300.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0142-367x275.jpg 367w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0142-200x150.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n			<h2>NEED HELP?</h2>		\n			<p>Our team at Ngeay Ngeay can take care of all your registration needs</p>		\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/kh/%e1%9e%91%e1%9f%86%e1%9e%93%e1%9e%b6%e1%9e%80%e1%9f%8b%e1%9e%91%e1%9e%84%e1%9e%99%e1%9e%be%e1%9e%84/\" role=\"button\">\n						Contact Us\n					</a>', 'Registering a Business Checklist good', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2076-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-07-26 19:06:03', '2019-07-26 12:06:03', '', '2076', 'http://maskred.com/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay/2019/07/26/2076-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `nge_posts` VALUES('2079', '1', '2019-07-26 19:07:19', '2019-07-26 12:07:19', '<h2>Starting a Business</h2>		\n		<p>What you need to know before you start</p>\n				<h3>\n					Why are you starting the <br><br>business?\n				</h3>\n				<p>It is very important when you start your business that you know why you are starting it, starting and operating a business is a huge challenge and you can never be 100% prepared for how much hard work it is. Because it is so challenging, it is important to know why you are starting the business, to keep you on track when you face these challenges.<br></p>\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/kh/why-are-you-starting-a-business__trashed/\" role=\"button\">\n						Read more here\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5904-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5904-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5904-300x200.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5904-768x512.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5904-640x427.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5904-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5904-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					Who is your target market?\n				</h3>\n				<p>This is one of the most important questions you can answer when developing your business model, with out a clear target market your business will struggle. If you try to please everybody you will please no one. Your target market needs to be as specific as possible.\nFor more on defining your target market, click below to go to our e-learning platform</p>\n			<a href=\"learn.ngeayngeay.co\" role=\"button\">\n						Learn more\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5160-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5160-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5160-300x200.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5160-768x512.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5160-640x427.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5160-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5160-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					What is your Value <br><br>Proposition?\n				</h3>\n				<p>The value proposition, is a promise of value to be delivered and communicated to your customer. What is the value you will deliver to your target market.\nWhy would your target market buy your product or service and not go to a competitor?\nFor more on this topic go to our e-learning platform</p>\n			<a href=\"learn.ngeayngeay.co\" role=\"button\">\n						Learn more\n					</a>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5898-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5898-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5898-300x200.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5898-768x512.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5898-640x427.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5898-400x267.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_5898-367x245.jpg 367w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n				<h3>\n					When will you launch?\n				</h3>\n				<p>Having clear timelines around your product development, testing and manufacturing is very important to ensure you can have enough cash flow when beginning your business. How long will it take to be financially sustainable? </p>\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-300x225.jpg 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-768x576.jpg 768w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-463x348.jpg 463w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-640x480.jpg 640w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-400x300.jpg 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-367x275.jpg 367w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/IMG_0177-200x150.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n			<h2>How?</h2>		\n			<figure><a href=\"/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay?p=1950\"><img width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465237060_resolutions-11.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465237060_resolutions-11.png 64w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465237060_resolutions-11-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 64px) 100vw, 64px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay?p=1950\">Clear Business Model</a></h3><p>For more information go to our article on business models and watch our Business Model Canvas series on the E-learning platform</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay?p=1958\"><img width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465236987_resolutions-16.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465236987_resolutions-16.png 64w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/1465236987_resolutions-16-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 64px) 100vw, 64px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"/BIGkeenProject/BK_ngeayngeay?p=1958\">Complete a Budget</a></h3><p>See our article and template here on completing a budget</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"h