ment-bank-money-money-icon-png-5ab065b43cec57.4598047615215098122496.png 512w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/kisspng-computer-icons-investment-payment-bank-money-money-icon-png-5ab065b43cec57.4598047615215098122496-150x150.png 150w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/kisspng-computer-icons-investment-payment-bank-money-money-icon-png-5ab065b43cec57.4598047615215098122496-300x300.png 300w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/kisspng-computer-icons-investment-payment-bank-money-money-icon-png-5ab065b43cec57.4598047615215098122496-400x400.png 400w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/kisspng-computer-icons-investment-payment-bank-money-money-icon-png-5ab065b43cec57.4598047615215098122496-367x367.png 367w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/kisspng-computer-icons-investment-payment-bank-money-money-icon-png-5ab065b43cec57.4598047615215098122496-85x85.png 85w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/kisspng-computer-icons-investment-payment-bank-money-money-icon-png-5ab065b43cec57.4598047615215098122496-50x50.png 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 512px) 100vw, 512px\" /></figure><h3>Proof of Capital</h3><p>Once you have opened your business bank account, you need a letter from the bank confirming your initial capital</p>		\n			<h3>Confused? We can Help </h3>		\n							<p>“Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut elit tellus, luctus nec ullamcorper mattis dapibus”</p>\n							<img width=\"346\" height=\"309\" src=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/about2-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/about2-1.jpg 346w, http://ngeayngeay.co/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/about2-1-300x268.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 346px) 100vw, 346px\" />						\n													Sara Johnon\n																			MG CEO\n							<p>\"Mauris sodales congue massa, vitae accumsan dolor efficitur in. Suspendisse volutpat, ipsum a aliquet\"</p>\n							<img width=\"345\" heig