w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 128px) 100vw, 128px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/business-licences/\">6. Obtain Business Licences</a></h3>		\n			<h2>Need Help?<br>Contact Us Now</h2>		\n			<a href=\"http://ngeayngeay.co/contact-us/\" role=\"button\">\n						Contact Us\n					</a>', 'Registration Summary', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2132-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-07-31 10:04:41', '2019-07-31 03:04:41', '', '2132', 'http://ngeayngeay.co/2019/07/31/2132-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
